---
import PublicLayout from '@/layouts/PublicLayout.astro';

export const prerender = true;
---

<PublicLayout
  title="Booking Conditions — Springbok Expeditions"
  description="Springbok Expeditions booking conditions. Payment, cancellation, travel insurance, and what to expect from your booking."
>
  <section class="section bg-dusk-50">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <p class="eyebrow text-safari-600 mb-3">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="text-display-sm md:text-display-md font-display font-medium tracking-tight text-safari-900 mb-4">
        Booking Conditions
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-dusk-500 mb-8">Last updated: January 2026</p>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-dusk-100 p-8 md:p-10 space-y-8 text-dusk-700 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          These booking conditions form part of your contract with Springbok Expeditions. They apply to all trips we operate, unless we have agreed something different in writing. We keep them short and clear — please read them.
        </p>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-safari-900 mb-3">1. The contract</h2>
          <p>A booking is confirmed when:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-2">
            <li>You accept a written quote from us</li>
            <li>You pay the deposit (30% of the trip cost)</li>
            <li>We send a written booking confirmation</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">The contract is between you (the lead traveller) and Springbok Expeditions, governed by the laws of Tanzania.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-safari-900 mb-3">2. Payment</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Deposit:</strong> 30% of the trip cost, due at booking.</li>
            <li><strong>Balance:</strong> 70%, due 60 days before the trip starts.</li>
            <li>For trips booked within 60 days of departure, full payment is due at booking.</li>
            <li>Bank transfer (no fee), or credit card (2% processing fee).</li>
            <li>You can pay in instalments between booking and the balance date.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-safari-900 mb-3">3. What's included</h2>
          <p>Your quote and booking confirmation list exactly what is included. As a guide, our standard inclusions are:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-2">
            <li>Accommodation as listed in the itinerary</li>
            <li>All meals from arrival to departure (as listed)</li>
            <li>Private 4x4 vehicle and English-speaking driver-guide for the duration of the safari</li>
            <li>Park and conservation fees for all parks and reserves in the itinerary</li>
            <li>Airport transfers on arrival and departure</li>
            <li>Bottled water in the vehicle</li>
            <li>Internal flights as listed in the itinerary</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-safari-900 mb-3">4. What's not included</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>International flights (we can recommend but not book)</li>
            <li>Travel insurance (mandatory — see below)</li>
            <li>Visas, vaccinations, and any medical costs</li>
            <li>Drinks (alcoholic and premium soft drinks) at lodges</li>
            <li>Tips for guides and lodge staff (we provide guidelines)</li>
            <li>Personal expenses (laundry, phone calls, souvenirs, spa)</li>
            <li>Optional activities not listed in the itinerary</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-safari-900 mb-3">5. Cancellation by you</h2>
          <p>If you need to cancel, the following charges apply (as a percentage of the trip cost):</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-2">
            <li>60+ days before departure: deposit refundable, minus bank charges</li>
            <li>30–59 days before: 50% of total cost</li>
            <li>15–29 days before: 75% of total cost</li>
            <li>Less than 15 days or no-show: 100% of total cost</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">If we can re-sell your dates, we will refund the full amount minus bank charges. We strongly recommend travel insurance to cover cancellation.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-safari-900 mb-3">6. Changes by you</h2>
          <p>If you want to change dates, route, or group size after booking, we will do our best to accommodate. Date changes more than 60 days before departure are usually free; changes within 60 days may incur supplier fees. Route or group-size changes are quoted case-by-case.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-safari-900 mb-3">7. Cancellation or changes by us</h2>
          <p>We very rarely cancel trips. When we do, it is usually for genuine safety reasons (severe weather, political instability) or because minimum numbers are not met. If we cancel:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-2">
            <li>You can take a full refund, or</li>
            <li>You can move to alternative dates at no extra cost</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">We do not refund additional costs you have incurred (international flights, visas, insurance) — please make these refundable where possible.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-safari-900 mb-3">8. Travel insurance</h2>
          <p>Travel insurance is mandatory for all our trips. Your policy must cover:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-2">
            <li>Trip cancellation and curtailment</li>
            <li>Medical expenses and emergency evacuation (specifically including air evacuation from a remote safari camp)</li>
            <li>Personal liability</li>
            <li>Loss of baggage and personal items</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">Please send us your policy details at least 30 days before departure.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-safari-900 mb-3">9. Your responsibilities</h2>
          <p>You are responsible for:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-2">
            <li>A valid passport (6+ months, 2+ blank pages)</li>
            <li>Any required visas and travel documents</li>
            <li>Following reasonable guidance from your driver-guide, lodge staff, and our team</li>
            <li>Obtaining appropriate vaccinations and anti-malarial medication</li>
            <li>Comprehensive travel insurance</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-safari-900 mb-3">10. Complaints</h2>
          <p>If something goes wrong on the trip, please tell your guide or our office immediately. Most issues can be resolved on the spot. If we can't resolve it during the trip, please email us within 28 days of return with your booking reference and a brief description. We will respond within 14 days and, where appropriate, offer a fair resolution.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-safari-900 mb-3">11. Our liability</h2>
          <p>We take responsibility for the services we provide as principal. Where services are provided by third parties (airlines, lodges, park authorities), we pass through their liability terms. Our maximum liability is limited to the cost of your trip with us.</p>
          <p class="mt-2">Nothing in these conditions limits our liability for death or personal injury caused by our negligence, or for fraudulent misrepresentation.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-safari-900 mb-3">12. Data protection</h2>
          <p>How we handle your personal data is set out in our <a href="/legal/privacy" class="text-safari-700 underline hover:text-safari-900">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-safari-900 mb-3">13. Contact</h2>
          <p>Springbok Expeditions · Arusha, Tanzania · <a href="mailto:info@springbokexpeditions.com" class="text-safari-700 underline hover:text-safari-900">info@springbokexpeditions.com</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PublicLayout>
